data.description: Welcome home to this charming Oak Harbor Estates community! Lovely wooded lot in the Eagle Mountain Lake side community with amenities for the entire family. Beautiful home with open concept and crown moldings with high ceilings boasts 3 Bedrooms, 1 Study which could be a 4th Bedroom, Spacious Living Room with gas log fireplace with switch, 2 Dinning Rooms with gorgeous wood flooring throughout, SS appliances in Kitchen with walk in pantry, back outdoor living area for entertaining with rod iron fenced yard and side entry garage. Community amenities includes a boat ramp, playground, sand volleyball, restrooms. Lovely neighborhood with curbs and side walks for daily walks.
